articles.title: Twitter neighbours complain of lit-up 'X' sign working at high intensity - The Guardian
articles.description: New logo for Elon Musk’s social network strobes over San Francisco neighbourhood, prompting complaints and mobilising building inspectors
articles.content: A giant glowing X marks the San Francisco spot where Elon Musk says he plans to keep his company, the messaging platform formerly known as Twitter. But city officials and some residents are unhappy w… [+3524 chars]
